OL,3,CDriver who flipped car over roundabout
OL,4,Cafter 140mph chase jailed
OL,6,FA dangerous driver who flipped his car
OL,7,Fover a roundabout after a high-speed
OL,8,Fpolice chase has been jailed.
OL,10,FAshley Parr, 35, hit speeds of 140mph
OL,11,Fin his BMW after failing to stop for
OL,12,Fpolice on the A64 near York on 21 July
OL,13,Flast year.
OL,15,FHe sped south along the A1 in North
OL,16,FYorkshire before leaving at junction
OL,17,F42, where he failed to negotiate a
OL,18,Froundabout.
