OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1776780669
OL,3,CDriver who flipped car over roundabout
OL,4,Cafter 140mph chase jailed
OL,6,FAfter hitting it at speed, the car
OL,7,Fbecame airborne and then rolled
OL,8,Fseveral times before coming to rest in
OL,9,Fa roadside hedge.
OL,11,FTraffic Constable Nick Simpson, of
OL,12,FNorth Yorkshire Police, said: "This
OL,13,Fwas extremely dangerous driving that
OL,14,Fcould easily have resulted in the
OL,15,Fdeath of other road users, as well as
OL,16,Fthe driver himself."
OL,18,FParr pleaded guilty to dangerous
OL,19,Fdriving, drug driving, and failing to
OL,20,Fstop for police.
